# Gunakan server actions untuk data mutation

Always use context7 MCP when referencing documentation for Next.js, 
React, Prisma, or any other library. Fetch docs automatically without 
being explicitly asked.

# Folder Exclusion Rules
# IMPORTANT: Exclude these folders from all operations (search, grep, analysis)
# - apps/           : Flutter project (162 files) - not relevant for Next.js admin panel
# - node_modules/   : Dependencies (36,440 files) - causes VS Code freeze
# Only scan relevant Next.js application code in src/, public/, and root configs

When performing any file operations (grep_search, file_glob_search, ls recursive):
- NEVER include apps/ folder
- NEVER include node_modules/ folder
- Focus on: src/, public/, .continue/, and root config files
- Example: Use patterns like 'src/**/*.tsx' instead of '**/*.tsx'